      }
  Step 4: Shutdown (Crucial!)
      If you don't shut down the executor, the JVM may never exit because the worker threads are still running.
      executor.shutdown();
      ✅ Graceful Shutdown
        executor.shutdown();
      ✅ Force Shutdown
          executor.shutdownNow();

