Happens-Before Rules:
  Program Order Rule- Within a thread → execution is in order
  Monitor Lock Rule (synchronized)- Unlock happens-before next lock
  Volatile Rule - Write to volatile → happens-before read
  Thread Start Rule- start() happens-before thread execution
  Thread Join Rule - Thread completion happens-before join()
  Final Field Rule - Final fields are safely published after constructor
  Transitivity Rule (Very Important) - If: A → B and B → C Then: 👉 A → C

